Package com.deliburd.extrataskschedulers

Interface StealingCallbackExecutorService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CallbackExecutorService, Executor, ExecutorService, StealingExecutorService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StealingCallbackExecutor
    public interface StealingCallbackExecutorService
extends StealingExecutorService, CallbackExecutorService
    An interface that specifies an ExecutorService that merges the StealingExecutorService and CallbackExecutorService interfaces and provides overridden task submission methods that return StealingCallbackFutures.
    Author:
    DELIBURD
